                <fr:title text="Local distributive lattice">Local distributive lattice</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is a <html:em>local</html:em> distributive lattice if (1) <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[0 \neq  1]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>; (2) for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a,b]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a \vee  b = 1]]></fr:tex> iff <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a = 1]]></fr:tex> or <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b = 1]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
