            <fr:title text="Boolean algebras only have maximal ideals">Boolean algebras only have maximal ideals</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Remark</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  By <fr:link href="/idem-comm-EV8L/" title="Quotient of prime filters are local" uri="https://www.my-great-forest.net/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" type="local">Proposition <fr:contextual-number uri="https://www.my-great-forest.net/idem-comm-EV8L/" display-uri="idem-comm-EV8L" /></fr:link> a distributive lattice <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is a <html:em>Boolean algebra</html:em> iff all prime ideals of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> are maximal.
</html:p>
